					<p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light leading-tight max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-ink);">Read the story for yourself</p>
					<p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed" style="font-family: var(--font-sans); color: var(--color-muted);">Start in the Gospel of John and read the good news in the Father&rsquo;s own voice &mdash; free online, with audio, in the Father&rsquo;s Heart Bible.</p>
					<a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/john/3" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-7 px-7 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold no-underline transition-opacity hover:opacity-90" style="background-color: #FFD9E0; color: #4A4A4A; font-family: var(--font-sans);">Read &amp; Listen Free<span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
				</aside>

