						Keep going: read <a href="/guides/how-to-read-the-bible/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">How to Read the Bible</a> and <a href="/guides/where-to-start-reading-the-bible/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Where to Start</a>, read <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/john/3" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">John 3 with audio</a>, learn <a href="/the-fathers-heart-bible/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">why the Father&rsquo;s Heart Bible exists</a>, or get the free book in the <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/library" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">resource library</a>. Browse <a href="/blog/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">the blog</a> for more.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

